### Get all Vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Vehicles
 
### Get Available Vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'
 
### Get all Drivers
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Drivers
 
### Get Drivers by Rating (Descending)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc
 
### Get all Customers
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Customers
 
### Get all Shipments
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments
 
### Get Shipments In Transit
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'
 
### Get Shipments of Specific Customer
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments?$filter=customerId eq '33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333331'
 
### Create Shipment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
    "ID": "44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444449",
    "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
    "customerId": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333331",
    "driverId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222221",
    "vehicleId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
    "pickupAddress": "77 Lake Avenue",
    "deliveryAddress": "Seattle Hub",
    "pickupCity": "Chicago",
    "deliveryCity": "Seattle",
    "weight": 250,
    "charges": 4500
}
 
### Update Shipment Status
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments(44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444449)
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
    "status": "Delivered"
}
 
### Get all Routes
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Routes
 
### Get Route Boston to Chicago
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Boston' and toCity eq 'Chicago'
 
### Get all Service Records
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/ServiceRecords
 
 